'''SSC''' waa koox argagixisa ah oo nabad diid ah lugna ku leh al-shabaab iyo al-qaida. Kooxdan argagixisada ahu waxay ku dhuumaaleystaan meelo u dhaxaysa [[Puntland]] iyo [[Somaliland]]. Argagaxisada SSC waxay sheegtaan gobolada [[Sool]], [[Sanaag]] iyo [[Cayn]]. Nimanka nabadiid yaasha ah ee SSC ma ahan maamul raadinooyo aqoonsi caalami ah ama is maamul gobol ahaan,balse loo samaystay sidii khal khal loo galin lahaa dowladaha [[puntland]] iyo [[somaliland]].Afayeenka kooxdan argagixisada ah waxa weeye saado cali warsame , halkaas oo ay ka keeneen magaca SSC.

23.2.2011 ayey beesha caalamku galisey SSC liiska ay ku jiraan kooxaha argagixisada ah sida Al-shabaab iyo Al-Qaida.
